# Cursor Rules - IT Ticket Analyzer UI Standards

## Project Overview
IT Ticket Analyzer - AI-powered ticket quality assessment and organization system with Phase 1-3 workflow

## Core Technologies
- **Framework**: React 18+ with TypeScript
- **UI Library**: Ant Design (antd)
- **Icons**: Lucide React (exclusively - NO Ant Design icons)
- **Styling**: CSS-in-JS with inline styles
- **Routing**: React Router DOM
- **HTTP Client**: Axios
- **Charts**: Recharts
- **State Management**: React Hooks (useState, useEffect)

## Design System

### Color Palette (CodeSpire Design System)
- **Primary**: #1268ff (CodeSpire Blue - for primary actions, links, and active states)
- **Primary Foreground**: #ffffff (white text on primary)
- **Primary Background**: #ffffff (white)
- **App Background**: #f9fafb (light background for layouts - slate-50)
- **Dark Base**: #101828 (deep navy/black for text and headers)
- **Text Primary**: #101828 (dark slate - main text)
- **Text Secondary**: #4a5565 (gray text - secondary/muted)
- **Text Tertiary**: #6a7282 (lighter gray text)
- **Borders**: #e5e7eb (light gray border)
- **Secondary Background**: #f2f4f7 (light gray for secondary areas)
- **Accent**: rgba(18, 104, 255, 0.08) (blue accent background)
- **Success**: #10b981 (green)
- **Warning**: #faad14 (orange)
- **Danger**: #ff4d4f (red)
- **Info**: #1890ff (light blue)
- **CodeSpire Blue 50**: #e6f0ff (very light blue)
- **CodeSpire Blue 100**: #cce1ff (light blue)
- **CodeSpire Blue 600**: #0f52cc (darker blue)
- **CodeSpire Blue 700**: #0b3d99 (even darker blue)
- **CodeSpire Blue 900**: #031763 (darkest blue)
- **CodeSpire Orange**: #ff6b1a (orange accent)
- **CodeSpire Purple**: #5700ff (purple accent)

### Typography (Inter Standard)
- **Font Family**: 'Inter', sans-serif (Exclusively for all UI elements and heads)
- **Titles**: `fontSize: '28px' to '36px'`, `fontWeight: 700`, `color: '#101828'`, `letterSpacing: '-0.02em'`
- **Subtitles**: `fontSize: '18px' to '20px'`, `fontWeight: 600`, `color: '#101828'`
- **Body Text**: `fontSize: '14px' to '15px'`, `color: '#4a5565'`
- **Small Caps/Labels**: `fontSize: '12px'`, `fontWeight: 700`, `textTransform: 'uppercase'`, `letterSpacing: '0.05em'`, `color: '#6a7282'`

### Spacing & Layout
- **Container Padding**: `24px`
- **Card Padding**: `24px` (content), `20px` (info cards)
- **Gap Between Elements**: `16px` (primary), `12px` (secondary), `8px` (tertiary)
- **Margin Bottom**: `24px` (sections), `16px` (sub-sections)
- **Border Radius**: `12px` (cards), `16px` (upload areas), `8px` (small elements)

### Shadows & Depth (CodeSpire Shadows)
- **CodeSpire Shadow**: `boxShadow: '0 8px 16px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.06)'`
- **CodeSpire Large Shadow**: `boxShadow: '0 12px 24px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08)'`
- **Hover Shadow**: `boxShadow: '0 12px 24px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08)'`
- **Subtle Shadow**: `boxShadow: '0 1px 0 rgba(3, 23, 99, 0.04)'`
- **Standard Card**: Always use **CodeSpire Shadow** for main layout divs and dashboard cards.

### Border Styles
- **Standard Border**: `border: '1px solid #e5e7eb'`
- **Header Border**: `borderBottom: '1px solid #e5e7eb'`
- **Thick Border**: `border: '2px solid #d1d5db'`

### Responsive Breakpoints (Ant Design)
- **Mobile**: `xs={24}` (full width)
- **Tablet**: `sm={12}`, `md={12}` (half width)
- **Desktop**: `md={8}`, `lg={6}`, `lg={4.8}` (proportional widths)
- **Large Screen**: Use proportional values for balanced layout

## Component Standards

### Card Components
```typescript
// Standard Info Card
<Card style={{
  border: '1px solid #e5e7eb',
  borderRadius: '12px',
  background: '#ffffff',
  boxShadow: '0 8px 16px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.06)',
  padding: '20px',
}}>
```

### Button Standards
- **Primary Action**: `background: '#1268ff'`, `color: '#ffffff'`, `height: '44px'`, `fontSize: '14px'`, `fontWeight: 500`
- **Secondary Action**: `color: '#101828'`, `borderColor: '#e5e7eb'`, `background: '#ffffff'`
- **Success/Accept**: `background: '#10b981'`, `borderColor: '#10b981'`, `color: '#ffffff'`
- **Danger/Reject**: `background: '#ff4d4f'`, `borderColor: '#ff4d4f'`, `color: '#ffffff'`, `danger` prop
- **Icon Size**: Always use `width={16} height={16}` for Lucide icons

### Icon & Sidebar Standards
- **Icon Library**: Use ONLY Lucide React.
- **Icon Container**: Icons typically sit in a **Primary (#1268ff)** background container.
- **Icon Color**: Use **#ffffff** (white) for icons in colored containers.
- **Sidebar Interaction**:
  - **Inactive**: Transparent background, slate text (#4a5565).
  - **Active/Selected**: **Primary (#1268ff)** background, **White (#ffffff)** text.
  - **Hover (Any state)**: **Primary (#1268ff)** background, **White (#ffffff)** text.
- **Board Depth**: All main content containers use the **CodeSpire Shadow** and `borderRadius: '12px'`.

### Progress & Loading
- **Loading State**: Use Ant Design `Skeleton` component with `paragraph={{ rows: X }}`
- **Progress Bars**: Custom styled divs with gradient background using CodeSpire blue (`background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #1268ff 0%, #40a9ff 100%)'`)
- **Success States**: Show checkmark icon and success message with `#10b981` color
- **Primary Color Progress**: Use `#1268ff` for progress indicators and completion states

